{"word":"G2450 - Ἰουδαΐζω - Ioudaḯzō - ee-oo-dah-id'-zo - Live as the Jews","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">Ἰουδαΐζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">Ioudaḯzō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ee-oo-dah-id'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Live as the Jews</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - யூத முறைமையாக நட"},{"paragraph":"to adopt Jewish customs and rites, imitate the Jews, Judaize"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2453 - Ἰουδαῖος - Ioudaîos - ee-oo-dah'-yos/2453\">G2453</a>; to <i>become a Judaean</i>, that is, &ldquo;judaize&rdquo;: - live as the Jews.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2448/2448\">G2448</a>, <a href=\"#/G2449/2449\">G2449</a>, <a href=\"#/G2450/2450\">G2450</a>, <a href=\"#/G2451/2451\">G2451</a>, <a href=\"#/G2452/2452\">G2452</a>, <a href=\"#/G2453/2453\">G2453</a>, <a href=\"#/G2454/2454\">G2454</a>"}]}